<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA10">
<l>eṉakkiṉiya vemmāṉai yīcaṉaiyā ṉeṉṟu</l>
<l>maṉakkiṉiya vaippāka vaittē - ṉeṉakkavaṉaik</l>
<l>koṇṭēṉ pirāṉākak koḷvatumē yiṉpuṟṟē</l>
<l>ṉuṇṭē yeṉakkariya toṉṟu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I have forever placed my master, the lord, who is pleasing to me,</l>
<l>as a deposed treasure that is pleasing to the mind. I have taken</l>
<l>him as my lord and feel pleasure in the taking.</l>
<l>Is there anything difficult for me [now]?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
